name: Chest Sarashi
description: This is a model that's based on the sarashi commonly seen on gangster type characters. Tends to work best at around 0.5-0.6. If just chest sarashi tends to do solid cloth, if bandages are included does one in more of a gauze like style. This model was trained on WarriorMama777's orange mix from huggingface. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.
